{"tid":1788152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係「革命」定「運動」？","createTime":"2019-12-18T12:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T17:15:33.000Z","uid":129351,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2d2dff97ecba05a781b23a37ee5d6bfeaaa0e77c","tid":1788152,"uid":129351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"所有人都會嗌「時代革命」，但又會叫「呢場運動」，真有趣。<br />\n<br />\n革命係從根本上嘅體制變革嘅一種嘗試。大家又有冇呢種心理建設？<br />\n<br />\n講革命，咁大家心入面又有冇想像過香港應然如何？係想重建一個新嘅制度，定只係想改善個制度？<br />\n<br />\n大家想像不同嘅話，又如何談得上係同路人？如果共同嘅心理特徵只有拒共，又係咪反動嘅民粹？"},{"pid":"b9ccedd3527352c281196c7e07df4f6ee88de8ad","tid":1788152,"uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:26:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代運動??<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港特式既革命"},{"pid":"14f1b89e9d07a01132ab81eb93396b94d4474fd8","tid":1788152,"uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"運動 如果咁都叫革命<br />\n咁化朝一日反抗更激烈嘅時候應該點叫？"},{"pid":"30df2bf4d40de34719525f00df7e071476d528d4","tid":1788152,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"工業革命？"},{"pid":"8b581aa67c2411600f6b1f7f12afd132245f21fb","tid":1788152,"uid":229886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14f1b89e9d07a01132ab81eb93396b94d4474fd8","tid":1788152,"uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"運動 如果咁都叫革命<br />\n咁化朝一日反抗更激烈嘅時候應該點叫？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T12:32:05.000Z","msg":"一定要有軍火先叫革命？<br />\n宜家由下而上既推翻政權<br />\n唔叫革命叫咩？"},{"pid":"14f29437b75649cf68f732a28999286f97a703ab","tid":1788152,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8b581aa67c2411600f6b1f7f12afd132245f21fb","tid":1788152,"uid":229886,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14f1b89e9d07a01132ab81eb93396b94d4474fd8","tid":1788152,"uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"